                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <span class="benefit-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                  <h5>Safest Method</h5>
                  <p>Direct visualization eliminates risk of eardrum damage</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <span class="benefit-icon">üíß</span>
                  <h5>No Water</h5>
                  <p>Completely dry procedure - no mess or discomfort</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <span class="benefit-icon">‚ö°</span>
