              </div>
              <div class="consideration-item">
                <h4>Recurrent Infections</h4>
                <p><strong>Recommended:</strong> Microsuction (dry method)</p>
                <p><strong>Avoid:</strong> Water-based methods during active infection</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="guide-section">
            <h3>Wax Type Considerations</h3>
